WEBVTT

00:03.724 --> 00:07.809
So, what do I have to do
to get you to, you know,

00:07.811 --> 00:09.478
to go out with me?

00:09.480 --> 00:13.315
What do you call this?

00:13.317 --> 00:15.317
Being neighborly.

00:17.655 --> 00:19.738
I'm taking about a real date, Maria.

00:19.740 --> 00:23.325
We both get dolled up, I take you out.

00:23.645 --> 00:27.079
Dinner, dancing. People still do that?

00:27.081 --> 00:29.248
Yeah, the old-fashioned ones.

00:29.250 --> 00:31.083
Those are my favorite kind.

00:31.085 --> 00:33.218
I like that about you.

00:35.000 --> 00:41.074
